15":"“dhammesu dhammanupassanasatipatthana”. ","ps3.8:14.1":"<b>Bhavana</b>ti catasso bhavana—","ps3.8:14.2":"tattha jatanam dhammanam anativattanatthena bhavana, indriyanam ekarasatthena bhavana, tadupagaviriyavahanatthena bhavana, asevanatthena bhavana. ","ps3.8:14.3":"Evam dhammesu dhammanupassi viharatiti. ","ps3.8:14.4":"Satipatthanakatha nitthita. "}